Demo-application "chat" 
========================

This application shows, implements long poll to push messages to the client.

This example uses the library mode of tntnet. We get a standalone application.
To run the application enter "./chat" in this directory.

You can see the result in your browser at http://localhost:8000/chat

Open 2 browsers and enter some text into the text box and press the send
button. Both browsers receive the message.

To see log output create a file "log.properties" with the content:
    rootlogger=INFO

Using a editor or by entering the command:
    echo rootlogger=INFO > log.properties
